 UFC 259: Israel Adesanya Loses For The First Time To Jan Blachowicz Nigerian kick boxer and UFC title holder, Israel Adesanya has lost his match against Polish MMA fighter, Jan Blachowicz. Israel Adesanya was defeated for the first time in a 5-round contest in the Light heavyweight division but he reportedly maintains his middleweight titles. Blachowicz won by a unanimous decision 49-45, 49-45, 49-46, win the first three rounds he utterly dominated Isreal.